# Political Party Template
##Boostrap Ready , Gallery/Portfolio Template

This theme is a one page gallery/ portfolio theme for Bootstrap created by Lend Kelmendi. This theme features several content sections, a responsive portfolio/services grid , blog pages ,donation page, subscribe forms etc.

##Getting Started

To use this theme, choose one of the following options to get started:
Fork this repository on GitHub


##Bugs and Issues

Have a bug or an issue with this theme? Open a new issue here on GitHub or leave a comment on the template overview page at Start Bootstrap.
